nodes.text: This massage parlor was a business that had locations in slum district G17 and the lower market districts on the planet Coruscant during the Clone Wars. The one in the slum district was situated next to Lauli Wahlo's noodle shop, Chezdeze, Trueping's and a Noodle Bar diner. The other parlor was located in a marketplace, near the Coruscant droid spa.
The parlor specialized in the treatment of shoulder aches. Aurebesh neon signs, like "massage" and "shoulder aches", were used to attract potential customers.
